user_query: Compar teh numbr of clicks to convrsions ratio for campains endng afer Janury 2024 on Instagrm platfrm, and show only those with spend over 1000
sql_query:
WITH CampaignPerformance AS (
  SELECT
    c.campaign_name,
    m.clicks,
    m.conversions,
    m.spend
  FROM dim_campaign AS c
  JOIN fact_marketing AS m
    ON c.campaign_id = m.campaign_id
  WHERE
    c.platform = 'Instagram'
    AND c.end_date >= '2024-01-01'
    AND m.spend > 1000
)
SELECT
  campaign_name,
  clicks,
  conversions,
  spend,
  CAST(clicks AS FLOAT) / conversions AS click_to_conversion_ratio
FROM CampaignPerformance
ORDER BY
  click_to_conversion_ratio DESC;
